::Primal Prime::

    The Spark left the Matrix behind, heading through space and time to Past 
Earth. There it found a stasis pod with a protoform inside, combining with 
the spark of the protoform it created a new warrior. 
    He opened the hatch, his blue hand finding it's grip. Shaking his head he 
got up and walked out of the pod. He looked himself over. He was impressed 
with what he saw. Red arms, Red chest, blue lower legs. He felt he needed to 
test his abilites. He thought about transforming and it happened, into a 
Ground Assult mode. He headed off toward the signal of the Maximals.
    Soon he found something he remembered faintly, the Ark. He walked up 
hoping that someone would find him.
